      "content": "<p><a href=\"https://eresearch.qmu.ac.uk/browse?type=author&amp;value=Mercer%2C+Tom\" title=\"Professor Tom Mercer - eResearch Repository QMU\" data-anchor=\"?type=author&amp;value=Mercer%2C+Tom\"><span class=\"blue-btn\">Professor Tom Mercer's research publications and outputs (QMU eResearch profile)</span></a></p>"
    },
